<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.lbl.gov/abc/">A link to the DoE's &quot;Division of Nuclear Physics&quot;..  Informative for those of us that might need it..  Easy to read, educational and gov't provided..  How much more valid can you get..?</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
